title: prada ​​dem

description.plain:
Prada Dem is the first single from Gunna’s fifth studio album One of Wun and sports a feature from Offset, marking the fourth official collaboration between the two Atlanta rappers. Although Gunna himself has appeared as a feature on a handful of songs since his release from prison in December 2022, Prada Dem is the first Gunna release with a featured artist since Gunna’s third studio album DS4EVER in January 2022.

The song was officially announced by Gunna in an Instagram post on March 14, 2024. It was initially teased by Gunna in an earlier post on March 12 where fans speculated that a new collaboration could be coming from the two artists. The music video was released on the same day as the track.
